snippet.title: Children of the Flower [Trailer]
snippet.description:
A little RPG made in 10 days for GBJAM 10!

Play for free in your browser: https://wombok.itch.io/children-of-the-flower

You are Daisy — spunky, ambitious, and totally fed up with your town's local cult and their "deity": a giant sunflower. Under the gaze of your powerful father, a gang of anarchists send you on a secret mission with an unspeakable objective... to exterminate the Godflower.

Art + programming: wombok (https://twitter.com/wombokgames)

Writing + music + logo: jermythemystic (https://www.instagram.com/jermythemystic/)

#gbstudio #gbjam10 #gamedev #indiedev #gameboy
